summary: add vampire power to Jenassa follower and facial vampire texture
descriptionHtml:
Jenassa, a great and strong dark elf woman and good warrior. I thought always to change something in her combat and power. So, i decided to become her a vampire. She\'s looking like a real vampire, and she plays like a very vampire. I added vampire power. She dont die when stays in day. She sometimes wont to hunt people for her thirsty so ... xD.
How to install
Manually: put on data skyrim main folder the files rar.
NMM: simply open NMM and add Jenassa vampire rar and active.
Be sure to they are active in lauch game folder. 
enjoy.
